{"tid":851908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鋼筋裝「蘑菇頭」防意外","createTime":"2018-10-07T13:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T14:09:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de86510a77d8e1e3125f458920eb718554fea246","tid":851908,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181007/20516555\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181007%2F20516555&d=56WQvXF2hEc6Lt4kRlG3gfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=b42c03e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181007%2F20516555&h=cb1de7ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181007/20516555</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月07日 <br />\n<br />\n鋼筋裝「蘑菇頭」防意外<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181007/large/07la5p21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181007%2Flarge%2F07la5p21.jpg&h=51d55429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】兩名工人昨日接連意外遭鋼筋插中受傷，工業傷亡權益會總幹事陳錦康表示，地盤外露的鋼筋一般非常鋒利，呼籲地盤負責人確保為鋼筋套上安全裝置，覆蓋鋒利的鋼筋頭，保障工人安全。<br />\n<br />\n過往同類意外不時發生，今年7月3日，一名工人在荔枝角工作時跣倒被鋼筋插穿左手臂；2013年9月17日青衣地盤一名工人釘板期間跌落兩米下的鋼筋，插破心臟重創昏迷不治。陳錦康表示，興建中的地盤滿佈外露鋼筋，通常插在石屎中準備接駁，由於鋼筋剪斷時不會打磨切口，因此鋼筋頭非常鋒利。他指現時普遍地盤未特別注意風險，只有部份地盤有實施保護措施。<br />\n<br />\n陳建議為外露的鋼筋頭套上俗稱「蘑菇頭」（圖）的鋼筋膠帽，或使用扁平的長條形膠套，以覆蓋鋒利的鋼筋頭，又呼籲地盤負責人盡早實施安全措施。另外，陳錦康促請地盤負責人清理地面雜物以保持整潔，免工人絆倒出意外。<br />\n<br />\n昨日其中一宗意外有工人從吊船墮下肇事，陳錦康提醒，工人在吊船上工作時應全程繫上安全帶，而安全帶需緊扣上獨立救生繩，以保障工人意外失足時，不會從吊船墮下。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李晟謙  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n10分鐘內先後跌下　鋼筋插穿身兩地盤工重創<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n菲總統秘密訪港疑治癌"},{"pid":"d522a6c2cfcb6bc0f8f8c714b25ee3f4a79d29fe","tid":851908,"uid":78016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"咁快開左間蘑菇頭公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7ac075a1380e2c6c1ff3d7caf1011912f965cb","tid":851908,"uid":61991,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d522a6c2cfcb6bc0f8f8c714b25ee3f4a79d29fe","tid":851908,"uid":78016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"咁快開左間蘑菇頭公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"不朽有呢d. 外國用左好多年啦，係香港人命賤如草，d安全野都無人會做"},{"pid":"cdb3e30eafd87efffc71458456ca9c2edfa710f5","tid":851908,"uid":35014,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"460540a5e3ca5c9cf6259020bdcc359f5d082897","tid":851908,"uid":5220,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:29:49.000Z","msg":"聽講D老屎忽嫌阻住做野<br />\n見到裝左會拆返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6742c97c13f143d8427b49b1f0e34fa0a0c6afa","tid":851908,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"460540a5e3ca5c9cf6259020bdcc359f5d082897","tid":851908,"uid":5220,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:29:49.000Z","msg":"聽講D老屎忽嫌阻住做野<br />\n見到裝左會拆返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"插死唔好怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f47ecc3b95c82c16e25006b2a2ca5dabcb1205","tid":851908,"uid":95,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"460540a5e3ca5c9cf6259020bdcc359f5d082897","tid":851908,"uid":5220,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:29:49.000Z","msg":"聽講D老屎忽嫌阻住做野<br />\n見到裝左會拆返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"華人賤種基因就係咁"},{"pid":"713b1a3432920d3e010ef6dbef22fd0214ea27fe","tid":851908,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu